# Inventory Management API

A production-oriented **ASP.NET Core Web API** built with **Clean Architecture**, **Vertical Slice Architecture**, **CQRS + MediatR**, **ASP.NET Identity**, **JWT Authentication**, **Refresh Token Rotation**, **Serilog**, and **Docker**.

The project focuses on maintainability, scalability, and modern backend development practices rather than a simple CRUD implementation.

---

## Features

### Architecture

* Clean Architecture
* Vertical Slice Architecture
* CQRS with MediatR
* Repository Pattern
* Dependency Injection
* FluentValidation Pipeline Behavior

### Authentication & Authorization

* ASP.NET Identity
* JWT Authentication
* Refresh Token Rotation
* Policy-based Authorization

### Product Management

* Create Product
* Update Product
* Delete Product
* Get Product by Id
* Get All Products

### Logging & Error Handling

* Global Exception Middleware
* Structured Logging with Serilog
* Console and File Logging

### Database

* Entity Framework Core
* SQLite
* Automatic EF Core Migrations on Startup

### DevOps

* Multi-stage Docker Build
* Docker Compose
* Persistent Database Volume
* Persistent Log Volume

---

## Architecture

```
                    Client
                       │
                       ▼
              ASP.NET Core API
                       │
        ┌──────────────┼──────────────┐
        ▼                             ▼
 Authentication                Product Module
        │                             │
        ▼                             ▼
 ASP.NET Identity              CQRS + MediatR
        │                             │
        └──────────────┬──────────────┘
                       ▼
                  Entity Framework
                       ▼
                    SQLite
```

